comments: Ingles (UTA) establishes a legal position in Martin's (CHA) path and firms up on his left leg when contact occurs.
Mitchell (UTA) dislodges Williams (CHA) from his legally obtained position during the drive.
Zeller (CHA) establishes a legal picking position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Zeller's (CHA) arm during his driving shot attempt that affects his ability to finish at the rim.
Rozier (CHA) makes marginal contact with Ingles's (UTA) body during his drive.
Rozier (CHA) cleanly dislodges the ball during Gobert's (UTA) upward shooting motion.
Zeller (CHA) and O'Neale (UTA) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Rozier (CHA) makes marginal contact with Mitchell's (UTA) body in the back court.
Williams (CHA) makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) arm during his shooting motion that affects the driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) makes incidental contact with Graham's (CHA) arm after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) clamps Gobert (UTA) affecting his ability to move to retrieve the rebound.
Gobert (UTA) briefly grasps Williams's (CHA) jersey but does not prevent him from defending the inbound.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact to Zeller's (CHA) arm during his shooting motion that affects the play at the basket.
null
Williams (CHA) makes marginal contact with Mitchell (UTA) at the end of the drive that does not affect his ability to pass.
Martin (CHA) makes contact to the arm of Gobert (UTA) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Graham (CHA) veers from his path and jumps away from the basket as he initiates contact with Ingles (UTA) affecting his ability to defend the play.
Zeller (CHA) establishes a legal position in O'Neale's (UTA) path during the screen and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Rozier (CHA) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Williams (CHA) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Graham's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
